---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us">

  <!-- PAGE HEADER -->
  <section class="about-header">
    <div class="header-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <span class="tag">Our Story</span>
      <h1>We Made Peanut<br/>Butter <em>RAD</em> Again.</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ORIGIN STORY -->
  <section class="section origin">
    <div class="container origin-inner">
      <div class="origin-text">
        <span class="tag">How It Started</span>
        <h2>Tired of Bad Peanut Butter</h2>
        <p>We grew up on peanut butter. Like, a <em>lot</em> of peanut butter. But somewhere along the way, the industry decided it was okay to sneak in palm oil, sugar, and weird stabilizers — and just hope nobody noticed.</p>
        <p>We noticed.</p>
        <p>So we set out to make peanut butter the way it should be: just peanuts, a pinch of sea salt, and absolutely nothing else you can't pronounce. We also figured out how to keep the oils perfectly blended without any additives — so you never have to stir again.</p>
        <p>That's it. That's RAD.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="origin-visual">
        <div class="origin-stat-card" style="--c: var(--pink)">
          <span class="stat-num">2</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Ingredients.<br/>That's All.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="origin-stat-card" style="--c: var(--cyan)">
          <span class="stat-num">0</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Palm Oil.<br/>Ever.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="origin-stat-card" style="--c: var(--yellow)">
          <span class="stat-num">∞</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Times More<br/>Delicious.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section class="section values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="tag">What We Stand For</span>
        <h2>The RAD <em>Promise</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon">📖</span>
          <h3>Radical Transparency</h3>
          <p>Every ingredient is on the label. We have nothing to hide and everything to be proud of. If it's not in the jar, it's not on the label.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon">🌍</span>
          <h3>Planet First</h3>
          <p>Palm oil contributes to deforestation. We won't touch it. Our packaging is recyclable, our peanuts are responsibly sourced, and we're always working to do better.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon">🔬</span>
          <h3>Obsessive Quality</h3>
          <p>We taste every batch. We tweak the roast. We obsess over texture. Because if we wouldn't eat it ourselves, we're not putting it in a jar with our name on it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-item">
          <span class="value-icon">💪</span>
          <h3>Fuel for Real Life</h3>
          <p>Whether you're a weekend warrior, a toddler with strong opinions, or someone who eats peanut butter straight from the jar — RAD is for you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROCESS -->
  <section class="section process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="tag">How It's Made</span>
        <h2>From Peanut to <em>Perfection</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">01</div>
          <h3>Sourced with Care</h3>
          <p>We partner with family-run peanut farms that share our obsession with quality. Only the best peanuts make it into a RAD jar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">02</div>
          <h3>Slow Roasted</h3>
          <p>Low and slow. Our roasting process brings out the deepest, richest peanut flavor without burning away the good stuff.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">03</div>
          <h3>Stone Ground</h3>
          <p>Ground in small batches on granite stone mills. Smooth when it should be smooth. Chunky when it should be chunky.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">04</div>
          <h3>Sealed Fresh</h3>
          <p>No preservatives needed — sealed airtight the moment it's perfect, and shipped straight to your door.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Taste What RAD Means.</h2>
      <p>Stop settling for ordinary peanut butter. Life is too short for jars full of mystery ingredients.</p>
      <a href="/products" class="btn btn-yellow">Shop Now ⚡</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .about-header {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--black);
    padding: 6rem 2rem 5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 4px solid var(--cyan);
  }
  .header-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, var(--pink) 0, var(--pink) 2px, transparent 2px, transparent 12px),
      repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, var(--cyan) 0, var(--cyan) 2px, transparent 2px, transparent 12px);
    opacity: 0.04;
  }
  .about-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .about-header h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--cyan); }
  .about-header .tag { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  /* ── ORIGIN ── */
  .origin { background: var(--cream); }
  .origin-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .origin-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .origin-text p {
    color: #444; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .origin-text p em { font-style: italic; color: var(--pink); font-weight: 700; }
  .origin-visual {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem;
    position: sticky; top: 5rem;
  }
  .origin-stat-card {
    background: var(--black);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-left: 6px solid var(--c);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: var(--c);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .stat-label {
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* ── VALUES ── */
  .values-section { background: var(--white); }
  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }
  .section-header h2 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--pink); }
  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  .value-item {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 2px solid #e8e0d4;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .value-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--pink);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .value-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .value-item h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  .value-item p { color: #555; line-height: 1.65; font-size: 0.95rem; }

  /* ── PROCESS ── */
  .process-section { background: var(--black); }
  .process-section .section-header h2 { color: var(--white); }
  .process-section .section-header h2 em { color: var(--yellow); }
  .process-section .tag { background: var(--yellow); }
  .steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .step {
    flex: 1; min-width: 180px; max-width: 240px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    border: 2px solid #333;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .step:hover { border-color: var(--cyan); }
  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem; color: var(--cyan);
    line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .step h3 { color: var(--white); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
  .step p { color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .step-arrow {
    font-size: 2rem; color: var(--pink);
    align-self: center; padding: 0 0.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .about-cta {
    background: var(--pink);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--black);
  }
  .about-cta h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--black);
  }
  .about-cta p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 1rem auto 2rem;
    max-width: 500px; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .btn-yellow { background: var(--yellow); color: var(--black); font-size: 1.1rem; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .origin-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
    .origin-visual { position: static; }
    .steps { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .step-arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  }
</style>
